你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinanceResearch.fetch_articles', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.fetch_articles', 'description': 'This function fetches articles related to a specific topic from a specified source.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the articles, e.g., gold market psychology.'}, {'name': 'source', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The source of the articles, e.g., latest financial magazine.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of up to four relevant articles.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.get_historical_prices', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.get_historical_prices', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical price data for a specified commodity on a given date.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date for which to retrieve the historical prices, in YYYY-MM-DD format.'}, {'name': 'commodity', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the commodity, e.g., gold.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'prices', 'description': 'Historical price data for the specified commodity on the given date.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.get_real_time_price', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.get_real_time_price', 'description': 'This function retrieves the current real-time market price for a specified commodity.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'commodity', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the commodity, e.g., gold.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'price', 'description': 'The current real-time market price for the specified commodity.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.get_commodity_code', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.get_commodity_code', 'description': 'This function retrieves the commodity code for a specified commodity.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'commodity', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the commodity, e.g., gold.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'code', 'description': 'The commodity code for the specified commodity.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.get_investment_advice', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.get_investment_advice', 'description': 'This function provides investment advice based on a specified commodity code.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'commodityCode', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The commodity code for which to provide investment advice, e.g., XAU.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'Investment advice based on the specified commodity code.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinanceResearch.fetch_articles` 并传入 `topic` 和 `source`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinanceResearch.fetch_articles",
    "args": "{'topic': 'gold market psychology', 'source': 'latest financial magazine'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
